OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774620679
OL,3,CMP calls for review of police and CPS
OL,4,Cconduct in Lucy Letby case
OL,6,FAn MP has called for a review into the
OL,7,Fconduct of the police and the Crown
OL,8,FProsecution Service (CPS) in the way
OL,9,Fthey handled the case of Lucy Letby.
OL,11,FConservative former Cabinet minister
OL,12,FSir David Davis told ministers on 26
OL,13,FMarch that he is going to write to the
OL,14,FDirector of Public Prosecutions (DPP)
OL,15,FStephen Parkinson to make his request.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
