OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774620679
OL,3,CMP calls for review of police and CPS
OL,4,Cconduct in Lucy Letby case
OL,6,FLetby, from Hereford, is serving 15
OL,7,Fwhole life orders after she was
OL,8,Fconvicted at Manchester Crown Court of
OL,9,Fmurdering seven infants and attempting
OL,10,Fto murder seven others between June
OL,11,F2015 and June 2016.
OL,13,FThe babies were attacked by various
OL,14,Fmeans while Letby worked as a nurse on
OL,15,Fthe neonatal unit at the Countess of
OL,16,FChester Hospital.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774620679
OL,3,CMP calls for review of police and CPS
OL,4,Cconduct in Lucy Letby case
OL,6,FOne method was the injection of air
OL,7,Finto the bloodstream, causing an air
OL,8,Fembolism that blocked the blood supply
OL,9,Fand led to sudden and unexpected
OL,10,Fcollapses.
OL,12,FHowever, concerns have emerged that
OL,13,Fher conviction was a miscarriage of
OL,14,Fjustice, with Sir David branding it
OL,15,F"one of the major injustices of modern
OL,16,Ftimes" last year.
OL,18,FHer case is being reviewed by the
OL,19,FCriminal Cases Review Commission,
OL,20,Fafter judges rejected her bids to
OL,21,Fchallenge her convictions.
OL,26,@wD@AOUxD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
