PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774620679
OL,3,CMP calls for review of police and CPS
OL,4,Cconduct in Lucy Letby case
OL,6,FSpeaking in the House of Commons, Sir
OL,7,FDavid claimed Cheshire Police, who
OL,8,Finvestigated the Letby case, ignored
OL,9,For broke rules "time and time again".
OL,11,FHe called for the force to release a
OL,12,Fseries of documents, including
OL,13,Finvestigators' policy books and
OL,14,Fdecision books, records of identified
OL,15,Flines of inquiry and minutes from
OL,16,Fmeetings.
OL,26,@qD@POUqD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774620679
OL,3,CMP calls for review of police and CPS
OL,4,Cconduct in Lucy Letby case
OL,6,FThe former Brexit Secretary compared
OL,7,Fthe Letby case to that of Sally Clark,
OL,8,Fa woman who was found guilty of the
OL,9,Fmurder of her two infant sons, but
OL,10,Fwhose conviction was overturned three
OL,11,Fyears later.
OL,13,FThe prosecution had relied on flawed
OL,14,Fstatistical evidence about the
OL,15,Flikelihood of two babies in an
OL,16,Faffluent family both dying of sudden
OL,17,Finfant infant death syndrome (Sids).
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774620679
OL,3,CMP calls for review of police and CPS
OL,4,Cconduct in Lucy Letby case
OL,6,FSir David said: "Despite warning signs
OL,7,Fof the Sally Clark case, we see that
OL,8,FCheshire Police have either ignored or
OL,9,Fbroken the rules, disregarding
OL,10,Frelevant safeguards time and time
OL,11,Fagain.
OL,13,F"They failed to pursue alternative
OL,14,Flines of inquiry.
OL,16,F"They failed to refer the case to the
OL,17,Fappropriate specialist authorities.
OL,19,F"They failed to conduct proper due
OL,20,Fdiligence on the appointment of key
OL,21,Fwitnesses, expert witnesses.
OL,26,@nD@QOUuD@AOUxD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774620679
OL,3,CMP calls for review of police and CPS
OL,4,Cconduct in Lucy Letby case
OL,6,F"They failed to engage with real
OL,7,Fexperts about complex statistical
OL,8,Fevidence and failed to correctly
OL,9,Finform the jury of that fact.
OL,11,F"They failed, on several occasions, to
OL,12,Fdisclose critical material to the
OL,13,Fdefence.
OL,15,F"On the evidence before us, there have
OL,16,Fbeen clear, serious departures from
OL,17,Fstatutory guidance and multiple
OL,18,Fdeviations from best professional
OL,19,Fpractice."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774620679
OL,3,CMP calls for review of police and CPS
OL,4,Cconduct in Lucy Letby case
OL,6,FHe added: "Irrespective of how
OL,7,FCheshire Police respond, I should tell
OL,8,Fthe minister, I shall be writing to
OL,9,Fthe Director of Public Prosecution
OL,10,Fabout these issues and asking him to
OL,11,Freview the behaviour, both of the CPS
OL,12,Fand police."
OL,14,FPolicing minister Sarah Jones said
OL,15,Fthat "a meticulous and very lengthy
OL,16,Finvestigation" led to Letby being
OL,17,Fidentified as a suspect and arrested.
OL,26,@nD@KOUtD@LO]wD@FOUxD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774620679
OL,3,CMP calls for review of police and CPS
OL,4,Cconduct in Lucy Letby case
OL,6,FShe added that "there has been a
OL,7,Fproper process involving independent
OL,8,Fassessment by the CPS, trial by a
OL,9,Fjury, and two appeal processes that
OL,10,Fhas resulted in the conviction and
OL,11,Fimprisonment of Lucy Letby".
OL,13,FMs Jones also told the Commons: "We
OL,14,Fshouldn't inadvertently undermine
OL,15,Fpublic confidence in the police ` that
OL,16,Fis important and in the criminal
OL,17,Fjustice system and we need to be very
OL,18,Fcareful to avoid implying impropriety
OL,19,Fwhere none has actually been
OL,20,Festablished, and I need to put that on
OL,21,Frecord as well."
OL,26,@nD@POUsD@[O]uD@aOU}D@PO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774620679
OL,3,CMP calls for review of police and CPS
OL,4,Cconduct in Lucy Letby case
OL,6,FShe added: "Of course, (Sir David) has
OL,7,Fsaid that he is going to be writing to
OL,8,Fthe DPP and he will take that through
OL,9,Fits course.
OL,11,F"But I just want to end by reminding
OL,12,Fthe House that this country uses due
OL,13,Fprocess.
OL,15,F"There has been due process that has
OL,16,Fbeen followed in the convictions of
OL,17,FLucy Letby with a trial by jury and
OL,18,Fupheld on appeal, and I remain
OL,19,Fconfident of that and also the
OL,20,Feffectiveness of the Cheshire
OL,21,FConstabulary."
OL,26,@nD@LOUsD@AOUwD@AOU}D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
