CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774620679
OL,3,CMP calls for review of police and CPS
OL,4,Cconduct in Lucy Letby case
OL,6,FA Crown Prosecution Service
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "Lucy Letby was
OL,8,Fconvicted of 15 separate counts
OL,9,Ffollowing two jury trials.
OL,11,F"In May 2024, the Court of Appeal
OL,12,Fdismissed Letby's leave to appeal on
OL,13,Fall grounds ` rejecting her argument
OL,14,Fthat expert prosecution evidence was
OL,15,Fflawed."
OL,17,FCheshire Police has been contacted for
OL,18,Fcomment.
OL,26,@oD@TOUsD@AOUwD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/11
